column2: "Hey, you made it back in one piece, huh? Your report checks out, so I'd say everything went just fine."
"If you keep wielding twin daggers like that, you won't have anything to worry about."
"Oh, and go ahead and keep the twin daggers I gave you. "
"Well, see you around, pal. Keep practicing with those twin daggers!"

"A new Client Order is available for Barbara.

Barbara can be found in the Gate Area, second floor."
